OL,3,CCare home director 'upset and
OL,4,Cdisappointed' by Covid breach claims
OL,6,FThe director of a care home hit by a
OL,7,FCovid outbreak in which seven elderly
OL,8,Fresidents died was "upset and
OL,9,Fdisappointed" by how events unfolded,
OL,10,Fan inquest has heard.
OL,12,FThe residents, who lived at Holmesley
OL,13,FCare Home in Sidford, Devon, all died
OL,14,Fin March or April 2021 having
OL,15,Fcontracted coronavirus.
