OL,3,CCare home director 'upset and
OL,4,Cdisappointed' by Covid breach claims
OL,6,FThe inquest has heard evidence from
OL,7,FJemma Turner, the nursing home's
OL,8,Fdeputy manager, who alleged a night-
OL,9,Ftime nurse had refused to wear a
OL,10,Ffacemask and was claiming "Covid was a
OL,11,Fconspiracy".
OL,13,F24 February 2021 - Care assistant
OL,14,Ftests positive for Covid
OL,16,FOn 24 February 2021, a care assistant
OL,17,Fat the nursing home tested positive
OL,18,Ffor Covid-19 and began isolating at
OL,19,Fhome, the hearing at County Hall, in
OL,20,FExeter, heard.
