OL,3,CCare home director 'upset and
OL,4,Cdisappointed' by Covid breach claims
OL,6,FWilliam Neal, the nursing home's
OL,7,Fdirector, told the hearing he was not
OL,8,Fmade aware of the positive test at the
OL,9,Ftime, but that a Covid contingency
OL,10,Fplan was in place.
OL,12,FThe home guidelines said that if a
OL,13,Fstaff member tested positive, they
OL,14,Fshould be sent home, and then any
OL,15,Fresident they had been in close
OL,16,Fcontact with must isolate for 14 days
OL,17,Fand all staff and residents must be
OL,18,Ftested.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/16
