OL,3,CCare home director 'upset and
OL,4,Cdisappointed' by Covid breach claims
OL,6,FMr Neal told the inquest of one
OL,7,Foccasion where Mrs Burchell had
OL,8,Finformed him she had been left with no
OL,9,Fchoice but to ask a live-in care
OL,10,Fassistant, who was isolating after
OL,11,Ftesting positive for Covid-19, to work
OL,12,Fbecause of staff shortages.
OL,14,F"I felt very uneasy about this, but I
OL,15,Fwas not on the ground and Joanne
OL,16,FBurchell had to make the very hard
OL,17,Fchoice between the real dangers,
OL,18,Fpossibly choking or falling, on one
OL,19,Fhand, and Covid exposure on the
OL,20,Fother," he said.
