OL,6,F"With two people who were already
OL,7,FCovid positive, she felt that seemed
OL,8,Flike the less risk.
OL,10,F"I was quite shell-shocked by the
OL,11,Fconversation because it was very, very
OL,12,Fdifficult. She made the decision she
OL,13,Fmade in the best interests and overall
OL,14,Fsafety of the residents.
OL,16,F"I didn't like it and didn't really
OL,17,Fwant to do it but it was her decision
OL,18,Fas the care professional on the
OL,19,Fground."
