OL,6,FMr Neal said Mrs Burchell had told him
OL,7,Fthe care worker would be working on
OL,8,Fhis own and only with patients with
OL,9,FCovid-19.
OL,11,FAsked about the evidence of another
OL,12,Fnurse who alleged this care worker was
OL,13,Fin fact not wearing PPE and was seen
OL,14,Foutside the room of a non-Covid-19
OL,15,Fpositive resident, Mr Neal replied:
OL,16,F"That would be very shocking to me."
OL,18,F1 March 2021 - Six people test
OL,19,Fpositive for Covid
