OL,3,CCare home director 'upset and
OL,4,Cdisappointed' by Covid breach claims
OL,6,FOn 1 March, four residents and two
OL,7,Fstaff tested positive but it was put
OL,8,Fdown to a "bad batch of tests", the
OL,9,Fhearing heard.
OL,11,FWhen asked about this, Mr Neal said it
OL,12,Fwas "unthinkable" that six people were
OL,13,Fshowing symptoms and testing positive
OL,14,Fand it was ignored.
OL,16,FHe said: "I can't get my head around
OL,17,Fit. If that happened, that is really,
OL,18,Freally bad. Categorically, managers
OL,19,Fknew what they should be doing."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/16
