OL,3,CCare home director 'upset and
OL,4,Cdisappointed' by Covid breach claims
OL,6,F2 March 2021 - Potential second
OL,7,Foutbreak
OL,9,FThe inquest has heard that staff
OL,10,Frealised there was potentially an
OL,11,Foutbreak on the morning of 2 March,
OL,12,Fbut days before six positive results
OL,13,Fhad been ignored and attributed to a
OL,14,Fbad batch of tests.
OL,16,FMr Neal said he did not know any of
OL,17,Fthis until he was told days later by
OL,18,FMrs Turner in a whistleblowing email.
OL,20,FHe said: "When I did hear about that I
OL,21,Fthought that was unthinkable.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G10/16
