OL,3,CCare home director 'upset and
OL,4,Cdisappointed' by Covid breach claims
OL,6,F"The idea that six people would be
OL,7,Fcoughing, displaying symptoms of Covid-
OL,8,F19, and tested positive, and we just
OL,9,Fignored it and called the GP.
OL,11,F"I found that hard to process. I
OL,12,Fcannot get my head around how that
OL,13,Fhappened."
OL,15,FMr Neal told the hearing he regretted
OL,16,Fnot dismissing the nurse who was
OL,17,Frefusing to wear a mask after they had
OL,18,Fpreviously been told to use PPE after
OL,19,Fit was raised as a concern following a
OL,20,FCare Quality Commission inspection the
OL,21,Fprevious month.
