OL,6,FHe said: "I feel really upset and I
OL,7,Ffeel really disappointed. The
OL,8,Fsituation of not wearing a mask, when
OL,9,Fhe should have been wearing a mask
OL,10,Fappropriately, is really, really
OL,11,Fdisappointing to hear.
OL,13,F"Jemma did the one to one with him
OL,14,Fafter it was identified. Maybe we
OL,15,Fshould have an instant dismissal, and
OL,16,Fit is easy to say now we should have
OL,17,Fsacked him, but we had employment
OL,18,Frules and stuff like that.
OL,20,F"I wished we had dismissed at that
OL,21,Fpoint.
