OL,6,F"If it had been highlighted to me that
OL,7,Fhe was not wearing his mask after
OL,8,Fhaving had that conversation I would
OL,9,Fhave said he has to be suspended, and
OL,10,FI would have been saying get rid of
OL,11,Fhim.
OL,13,F"In terms of the six people who
OL,14,Fsupposedly had a positive LFT test on
OL,15,FMarch 1, if that happened that is
OL,16,Freally, really bad and I feel very
OL,17,Fdisappointed about that if that has
OL,18,Fhappened.
