OL,3,CCare home director 'upset and
OL,4,Cdisappointed' by Covid breach claims
OL,6,FJoanne Birchall, the nursing home's
OL,7,Fmanager, has not been summoned to
OL,8,Fappear at the inquest. The coroner
OL,9,Ftold the inquest she was invited as an
OL,10,Finterested party but opted not to
OL,11,Fattend.
OL,13,FThe inquest heard Ms Birchall was
OL,14,Fquestioned by police on 30 March 2021,
OL,15,Fduring their investigation into the
OL,16,Foutbreak.
OL,18,FDuring the investigation, she told
OL,19,Fpolice, that to her knowledge, no
OL,20,Fstaff who had tested positive came
OL,21,Finto contact with residents.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G15/16
