OL,3,CCare home director 'upset and
OL,4,Cdisappointed' by Covid breach claims
OL,6,FIn a prepared statement, she said: "I
OL,7,Ffirmly deny neglecting or ill treating
OL,8,Fresidents in any way."
OL,10,FThe inquest was told she was asked
OL,11,Fmore questions in a series of
OL,12,Finterviews during the police
OL,13,Finvestigation into the outbreak, to
OL,14,Fwhich she declined to comment.
OL,16,FNo charges were brought by the police
OL,17,Fand the investigation was closed.
OL,19,FThe inquest continues.
